text: Bought their luscious lychee for my son's birthday. Tasted so good. Worry free as one of my boy cannot consume nuts while the other no eggs allowed. The JellyHearts has no nuts no egg.

so kind of this lady name Hui Yu.
came to Novena branch at 9.10pm and was closed.
saw this lady carry her bag and walking out as she say shop closed end work .. so i ask if i could buy a box of 9pcs jelly..she is so kind she even served me even tho is after her work hour. and i manage to get 1 box.  5 STAR THUMB UP FOR THIS LADY.. Thank u very much Hui Yu.

It's definitely a nice alternative to your usual cakes. Whether it's for birthday, events, or just because. The cheesecake layer is nice, coupled with the jelly like top, and that heart shaped fruit cut out. It definitely reminds me of childhood. I really like how their boxes are packaged, sturdy, does the job, and has all the descriptions printed on it.
Lovely Kak kak Rafidah, is super friendly n cheerful alway give me suggestions to buy jellycake.. Happy to shop with her. She really make my day purchase with smile😊😊Good job kak Rafidah 👍👍
Ordered the jelly cake. Is very nice and my birthday fren loves it. 😀👍
